{"1":{"w":[{"b":"0.07","h":"1.05","c":"اقْتَرَبَتِ","d":"ِtَbَrَtْqٱ","e":"Telah dekat"},{"b":"1.3","h":"2.75","c":"السَّاعَةُ","d":"ُẗَʿعāَّslٱ","e":"saat itu"},{"b":"2.5","h":"4.64","c":"وَانْشَقَّ","d":"َّqَhsnٱَw","e":"telah terbelah"},{"b":"4.3","h":"6.92","c":"الْقَمَرُ","d":"ُrَmَqْlٱ","e":"bulan"}],"a":{"g":"The Hour has come near, and the moon has split [in two]."}},"2":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.15","c":"وَإِنْ","d":"nِiʾَw","e":"Dan jika"},{"b":"1.3","h":"1.44","c":"يَرَوْا","d":"۟āْwَrَy","e":"melihat"},{"b":"1.7","h":"2.4","c":"ءَايَةً","d":"ًẗَyāَء","e":"tanda (mu'jizat)"},{"b":"3.4","h":"4.53","c":"يُعْرِضُوا","d":"۟āwُḍِrْʿعُy","e":"mereka berpaling"},{"b":"4.5","h":"6.37","c":"وَيَقُولُوا","d":"۟āwُlwُqَyَw","e":"berkata"},{"b":"5.8","h":"8.36","c":"سِحْرٌ","d":"ٌrْḥِs","e":"(Ini adalah) sihir"},{"b":"7.9","h":"10.25","c":"مُسْتَمِرٌّ","d":"ٌّrِmَtْsُّm","e":"yang terus menerus"}],"a":{"g":"And if they see a miracle, they turn away and say, \"Passing magic.\""}},"3":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.65","c":"وَكَذَّبُوا","d":"۟āwُbَّhdَkَw","e":"Dan mereka mendustakan"},{"b":"1.3","h":"2.54","c":"وَاتَّبَعُوا","d":"۟āٓwُʿعَbَّtٱَw","e":"dan mengikuti"},{"b":"3.8","h":"5.56","c":"أَهْوَاءَهُمْ","d":"ْmُhَءٓāَwْhَaʾ","e":"nafsu mereka"},{"b":"7.3","h":"11.4","c":"وَكُلُّ","d":"ُّlُkَw","e":"sedang tiap-tiap"},{"b":"8.1","h":"12.62","c":"أَمْرٍ","d":"ٍrْmَaʾ","e":"urusan"},{"b":"10.","h":"14.69","c":"مُسْتَقِرٌّ","d":"ٌّrِqَtْsُّm","e":"ada ketetapannya"}],"a":{"g":"And they denied and followed their inclinations. But for every matter is a [time of] settlement."}},"4":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.08","c":"وَلَقَدْ","d":"ْdَqَlَw","e":"Dan sesungguhnya"},{"b":"0.81","h":"1.36","c":"جَاءَهُمْ","d":"mُhَءٓāَjg","e":"telah datang"},{"b":"3.9","h":"4.49","c":"مِنَ","d":"َnِّm","e":"dari"},{"b":"4.2","h":"5.05","c":"الْأَنْبَاءِ","d":"ِءٓāَbۢnَaʾْlٱ","e":"beberapa kisah"},{"b":"8.3","h":"8.61","c":"مَا","d":"āَm","e":"yang/apa-apa"},{"b":"8.7","h":"9.29","c":"فِيهِ","d":"ِhyِf","e":"di dalamnya"},{"b":"9.5","h":"10.6","c":"مُزْدَجَرٌ","d":"ٌrَjgَdْzُm","e":"terdapat cegahan (dari kekafiran)"}],"a":{"g":"And there has already come to them of information that in which there is deterrence -"}},"5":{"w":[{"b":"0.07","h":"0.45","c":"حِكْمَةٌ","d":"ٌۢẗَmْkِḥ","e":"itulah suatu hikmat"},{"b":"2.1","h":"2.41","c":"بَالِغَةٌ","d":"ٌẗَغِlَٰb","e":"yang sempurna"},{"b":"4.4","h":"5.1","c":"فَمَا","d":"āَmَf","e":"maka apa-apa"},{"b":"5.1","h":"6.31","c":"تُغْنِ","d":"ِnْغُt","e":"tiada berguna"},{"b":"5.9","h":"7.45","c":"النُّذُرُ","d":"ُrُhdُّnlٱ","e":"peringatan-peringatan"}],"a":{"g":"Extensive wisdom - but warning does not avail [them]."}},"6":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"1.3","c":"فَتَوَلَّ","d":"َّlَwَtَf","e":"Maka berpalinglah"},{"b":"0.96","h":"2.78","c":"عَنْهُمْ","d":"ْmُhْnَʿع","e":"dari mereka"},{"b":"2.5","h":"6.8","c":"يَوْمَ","d":"َmْwَy","e":"hari (ketika)"},{"b":"3.1","h":"7.72","c":"يَدْعُ","d":"ُʿعْdَy","e":"seorang penyeru"},{"b":"3.8","h":"8.8","c":"الدَّاعِ","d":"ِʿعāَّdlٱ","e":"menyeru"},{"b":"4.7","h":"10.66","c":"إِلَى","d":"ٰàَlِiʾ","e":"kepada"},{"b":"5.3","h":"11.42","c":"شَيْءٍ","d":"ٍءْàَhs","e":"sesuatu"},{"b":"6.9","h":"12.89","c":"نُكُرٍ","d":"ٍrُkُّn","e":"yang tidak menyenangkan"}],"a":{"g":"So leave them, [O Muhammad]. The Day the Caller calls to something forbidding,"}},"7":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.04","c":"خُشَّعًا","d":"āًʿعَّhsُhk","e":"sambil menundukkan"},{"b":"1.0","h":"1.48","c":"أَبْصَارُهُمْ","d":"ْmُhُrَٰṣْbَaʾ","e":"pandangan-pandangan"},{"b":"2.5","h":"3.86","c":"يَخْرُجُونَ","d":"َnwُjgُrْhkَy","e":"mereka keluar"},{"b":"3.9","h":"5.87","c":"مِنَ","d":"َnِm","e":"dari"},{"b":"4.3","h":"6.49","c":"الْأَجْدَاثِ","d":"ِhtāَdْjgَaʾْlٱ","e":"kuburan"},{"b":"5.6","h":"8.47","c":"كَأَنَّهُمْ","d":"ْmُhَّnَaʾَk","e":"seakan-akan"},{"b":"7.8","h":"10.72","c":"جَرَادٌ","d":"ٌdāَrَjg","e":"belalang"},{"b":"11.0","h":"13.02","c":"مُنْتَشِرٌ","d":"ٌrِhsَtnُّm","e":"beterbangan"}],"a":{"g":"Their eyes humbled, they will emerge from the graves as if they were locusts spreading,"}},"8":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.64","c":"مُهْطِعِينَ","d":"َnyِʿعِṭْhُّm","e":"datang dengan cepat"},{"b":"1.2","h":"2.3","c":"إِلَى","d":"àَlِiʾ","e":"kepada"},{"b":"1.6","h":"3.21","c":"الدَّاعِ","d":"ِʿعāَّdlٱ","e":"penyeru"},{"b":"4.5","h":"6.7","c":"يَقُولُ","d":"ُlwُqَy","e":"berkata"},{"b":"5.4","h":"8","c":"الْكَافِرُونَ","d":"َnwُrِfَٰkْlٱ","e":"Orang-orang kafir"},{"b":"6.9","h":"10.35","c":"هَذَا","d":"āَhdَٰh","e":"ini"},{"b":"7.8","h":"12.05","c":"يَوْمٌ","d":"ٌmْwَy","e":"hari"},{"b":"8.7","h":"13.43","c":"عَسِرٌ","d":"ٌrِsَʿع","e":"berat"}],"a":{"g":"Racing ahead toward the Caller. The disbelievers will say, \"This is a difficult Day.\""}},"9":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.4","c":"كَذَّبَتْ","d":"ْtَbَّhdَk","e":"mendustakan"},{"b":"0.98","h":"1.83","c":"قَبْلَهُمْ","d":"ْmُhَlْbَq","e":"sebelum mereka"},{"b":"2.0","h":"3.38","c":"قَوْمُ","d":"ُmْwَq","e":"kaum"},{"b":"2.7","h":"4.43","c":"نُوحٍ","d":"ٍḥwُn","e":"Nuh"},{"b":"4.1","h":"6.15","c":"فَكَذَّبُوا","d":"۟āwُbَّhdَkَf","e":"mendustakan"},{"b":"5.5","h":"8.25","c":"عَبْدَنَا","d":"āَnَdْbَʿع","e":"hamba Kami"},{"b":"6.6","h":"9.93","c":"وَقَالُوا","d":"۟āwُlāَqَw","e":"mengatakan"},{"b":"7.8","h":"11.76","c":"مَجْنُونٌ","d":"ٌnwُnْjgَm","e":"seorang gila"},{"b":"9.0","h":"14.18","c":"وَازْدُجِرَ","d":"َrِjgُdْzٱَw","e":"ancaman"}],"a":{"g":"The people of Noah denied before them, and they denied Our servant and said, \"A madman,\" and he was repelled."}},"10":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.75","c":"فَدَعَا","d":"āَʿعَdَf","e":"Maka dia mengadu"},{"b":"0.79","h":"2.03","c":"رَبَّهُ","d":"ٓۥُhَّbَr","e":"Rabbnya"},{"b":"3.3","h":"4.94","c":"أَنِّي","d":"àِّnَaʾ","e":"aku ini"},{"b":"4.8","h":"6.81","c":"مَغْلُوبٌ","d":"ٌbwُlْغَm","e":"orang yang dikalahkan"},{"b":"6.9","h":"9.59","c":"فَانْتَصِرْ","d":"ْrِṣَtnٱَf","e":"maka tolonglah (aku)"}],"a":{"g":"So he invoked his Lord, \"Indeed, I am overpowered, so help.\""}},"11":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.35","c":"فَفَتَحْنَا","d":"ٓāَnْḥَtَfَf","e":"Maka Kami bukakan"},{"b":"2.9","h":"1.69","c":"أَبْوَابَ","d":"َbَٰwْbَaʾ","e":"pintu-pintu"},{"b":"3.9","h":"5.2","c":"السَّمَاءِ","d":"ِءٓāَmَّslٱ","e":"langit"},{"b":"6.5","h":"7.79","c":"بِمَاءٍ","d":"ٍءٓāَmِb","e":"dengan air"},{"b":"10.8","h":"10.77","c":"مُنْهَمِرٍ","d":"ٍrِmَhْnُّm","e":"yang tercurah"}],"a":{"g":"Then We opened the gates of the heaven with rain pouring down"}},"12":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.4","c":"وَفَجَّرْنَا","d":"āَnْrَّjgَfَw","e":"memancarkan"},{"b":"1.2","h":"2.35","c":"الْأَرْضَ","d":"َḍْrَaʾْlٱ","e":"bumi"},{"b":"2.1","h":"3.63","c":"عُيُونًا","d":"āًnwُyُʿع","e":"mata air"},{"b":"4.0","h":"5.94","c":"فَالْتَقَى","d":"àَqَtْlٱَf","e":"maka bertemulah"},{"b":"4.9","h":"7.45","c":"الْمَاءُ","d":"ُءٓāَmْlٱ","e":"air-air"},{"b":"7.1","h":"9.75","c":"عَلَى","d":"ٰٓàَlَʿع","e":"atas"},{"b":"9.3","h":"11.94","c":"أَمْرٍ","d":"ٍrْmَaʾ","e":"urusan"},{"b":"11.2","h":"13.66","c":"قَدْ","d":"ْdَq","e":"sesungguhnya"},{"b":"11.6","h":"14.33","c":"قُدِرَ","d":"َrِdُq","e":"ditetapkan"}],"a":{"g":"And caused the earth to burst with springs, and the waters met for a matter already predestined."}},"13":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.6","c":"وَحَمَلْنَاهُ","d":"ُhَٰnْlَmَḥَw","e":"dan Kami angkut"},{"b":"1.4","h":"2.6","c":"عَلَى","d":"ٰàَlَʿع","e":"atas"},{"b":"2.2","h":"3.7","c":"ذَاتِ","d":"ِtāَhd","e":"memiliki"},{"b":"3.0","h":"4.89","c":"أَلْوَاحٍ","d":"ٍḥَٰwْlَaʾ","e":"papan"},{"b":"4.1","h":"7.36","c":"وَدُسُرٍ","d":"ٍrُsُdَw","e":"dan kayu"}],"a":{"g":"And We carried him on a [construction of] planks and nails,"}},"14":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.6","c":"تَجْرِي","d":"àِrْjgَt","e":"berlayar"},{"b":"0.84","h":"1.98","c":"بِأَعْيُنِنَا","d":"āَnِnُyْʿعَaʾِb","e":"dengan pemeliharaan Kami"},{"b":"2.3","h":"4.41","c":"جَزَاءً","d":"ًءٓāَzَjg","e":"balasan"},{"b":"5.2","h":"7.02","c":"لِمَنْ","d":"nَmِّl","e":"bagi orang-orang"},{"b":"6.7","h":"8.79","c":"كَانَ","d":"َnāَk","e":"adalah"},{"b":"7.4","h":"10","c":"كُفِرَ","d":"َrِfُk","e":"diingkari"}],"a":{"g":"Sailing under Our observation as reward for he who had been denied."}},"15":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"1.4","c":"وَلَقَدْ","d":"dَqَlَw","e":"dan sesungguhnya"},{"b":"0.62","h":"2.2","c":"تَرَكْنَاهَا","d":"ٓāَhَٰnْkَrَّt","e":"Kami telah jadikan"},{"b":"3.5","h":"6.09","c":"ءَايَةً","d":"ًẗَyāَء","e":"pelajaran"},{"b":"5.9","h":"9.6","c":"فَهَلْ","d":"ْlَhَf","e":"maka adakah"},{"b":"6.6","h":"10.55","c":"مِنْ","d":"nِm","e":"dari"},{"b":"8.0","h":"11.98","c":"مُدَّكِرٍ","d":"ٍrِkَّdُّm","e":"mengambil pelajaran"}],"a":{"g":"And We left it as a sign, so is there any who will remember?"}},"16":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.85","c":"فَكَيْفَ","d":"َfْyَkَf","e":"maka alangkah"},{"b":"0.82","h":"1.6","c":"كَانَ","d":"َnāَk","e":"adalah"},{"b":"1.4","h":"2.62","c":"عَذَابِي","d":"àِbāَhdَʿع","e":"azab-Ku"},{"b":"2.7","h":"4.42","c":"وَنُذُرِ","d":"ِrُhdُnَw","e":"dan ancamanKu"}],"a":{"g":"And how [severe] were My punishment and warning."}},"17":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.7","c":"وَلَقَدْ","d":"ْdَqَlَw","e":"dan sesungguhnya"},{"b":"0.79","h":"1.87","c":"يَسَّرْنَا","d":"āَnْrَّsَy","e":"telah Kami mudahkan"},{"b":"1.9","h":"3.59","c":"الْقُرْءَانَ","d":"َnāَءْrُqْlٱ","e":"Al-Qur'an"},{"b":"3.4","h":"5.74","c":"لِلذِّكْرِ","d":"ِrْkِّhdlِl","e":"untuk peringatan"},{"b":"4.4","h":"7.39","c":"فَهَلْ","d":"ْlَhَf","e":"maka adakah"},{"b":"5.1","h":"8.55","c":"مِنْ","d":"nِm","e":"dari"},{"b":"6.9","h":"10.03","c":"مُدَّكِرٍ","d":"ٍrِkَّdُّm","e":"orang-orang yang memikirkan"}],"a":{"g":"And We have certainly made the Qur'an easy for remembrance, so is there any who will remember?","ihya":"\n        <div class=\"ihya-tafsir-box\" style=\"margin-top: 15px; border-top: 1px solid #eee; padding-top: 10px;\">\n            <h5 style=\"color: #91740c; font-family: Cabin, sans-serif;\">Tafsir Al-Ihya</h5>\n            <div class=\"ihya-arabic\" style=\"font-family: IndoPak; font-size: 18px; text-align: right; margin-bottom: 10px; color: #555;\">\n                ولكونه حاضرا في القلب ومنسيا بالشغل عنه سمي الله تعالى جميع معارف الإيمان تذكرا فقال تعالى: ﴿ ولقد يسرنا القران للذكر فهل من مدكر ﴾ {} فهذا هو علاج الصبر عن الوساوس والشواغل وهو آخر درجات الصبر وإنما الصبر عن العلائق كلها مقدم على الصبر عن الخواطر.\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"ihya-english\" style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; color: #777;\">\n                Indeed, because it is present within the heart [qalb] yet forgotten due to preoccupation away from it, Allah the Exalted has named all the knowledges [ma'arif] of faith a remembrance [tadhkira]. Thus He, the Exalted, said: \"And We have certainly made the Qur'an easy for remembrance [dhikr]. So is there any who will remember [mudhakir]?\" (54:17). This, then, is the remedy for patience [sabr] from whisperings and preoccupations, and it is the final degree of patience. For indeed, patience from all attachments is a prerequisite for patience from passing thoughts.\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        "}},"18":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.85","c":"كَذَّبَتْ","d":"ْtَbَّhdَk","e":"telah mendustakan"},{"b":"1","h":"2.19","c":"عَادٌ","d":"ٌdāَʿع","e":"kaum 'Ad"},{"b":"2.7","h":"4.01","c":"فَكَيْفَ","d":"َfْyَkَf","e":"maka bagaimana/alangkah"},{"b":"3.6","h":"5.44","c":"كَانَ","d":"َnāَk","e":"adalah"},{"b":"4.3","h":"6.47","c":"عَذَابِي","d":"àِbāَhdَʿع","e":"azab-Ku"},{"b":"5.4","h":"8.65","c":"وَنُذُرِ","d":"ِrُhdُnَw","e":"dan peringatan/ancaman-Ku"}],"a":{"g":"'Aad denied; and how [severe] were My punishment and warning."}},"19":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.5","c":"إِنَّا","d":"ٓāَّnِiʾ","e":"sesungguhnya Kami"},{"b":"1.1","h":"3.19","c":"أَرْسَلْنَا","d":"āَnْlَsْrَaʾ","e":"Kami telah mengirimkan"},{"b":"4.2","h":"5.28","c":"عَلَيْهِمْ","d":"ْmِhْyَlَʿع","e":"atas mereka"},{"b":"5.3","h":"7.09","c":"رِيحًا","d":"āًḥyِr","e":"angin"},{"b":"6.8","h":"8.8","c":"صَرْصَرًا","d":"āًrَṣْrَṣ","e":"sangat kencang"},{"b":"8.6","h":"10.94","c":"فِي","d":"àِf","e":"pada"},{"b":"9.2","h":"11.73","c":"يَوْمِ","d":"ِmْwَy","e":"hari"},{"b":"9.8","h":"12.76","c":"نَحْسٍ","d":"ٍsْḥَn","e":"na'as/sial"},{"b":"11.6","h":"14.69","c":"مُسْتَمِرٍّ","d":"ٍّrِmَtْsُّm","e":"tetap/terus menerus"}],"a":{"g":"Indeed, We sent upon them a screaming wind on a day of continuous misfortune,","ihya":"\n        <div class=\"ihya-tafsir-box\" style=\"margin-top: 15px; border-top: 1px solid #eee; padding-top: 10px;\">\n            <h5 style=\"color: #91740c; font-family: Cabin, sans-serif;\">Tafsir Al-Ihya</h5>\n            <div class=\"ihya-arabic\" style=\"font-family: IndoPak; font-size: 18px; text-align: right; margin-bottom: 10px; color: #555;\">\n                ومن آياته الهواء اللطيف المحبوس بين مقعر السماء ومحدب الأرض يدرك بحس اللمس عند هبوب الرياح جسمه ولا يرى بالمين شخصه وجملته مثل البحر الواحد والطيور محلقة فى جو السماء ومستبقة سباحة فيه بأجنحتها كما تسبح حيوانات البحر فى الماء وتضطرب جوانبه وأمواجه عند هبوب الرياح كما تضطرب أمواج البحر فإذا حرك الله الهواء وجعله ريحا هابة فإن شاء جعله نشرابين يدى رحمته كما قال سبحانه وأرسلنا الرياح لواقح فيصل بحركته روح الهواء إلى الحيوانات والنباتات فتستعد للنماء وإن شاء جعله عذابا على العصاة من خليقته كما قال تعالى إنا أرسلنا عليهم ريحا صرصرا فى يوم نحس مستمر تنزع الناس كأنهم أعجاز نخل منقعر\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"ihya-english\" style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; color: #777;\">\n                And from His signs [ayat] is the subtle air [al-hawa' al-latif], confined between the concave of the sky and the convex of the earth. Its substance is perceived by the sense of touch when the winds blow, yet its form is not seen by the eye. Its totality is like a single sea, and the birds soar in the atmosphere of the sky, racing in swimming through it with their wings, just as the creatures of the sea swim in water. And its sides and its waves are agitated when the winds blow, just as the waves of the sea are agitated. So when God sets the air in motion and makes it a blowing wind, then if He wills, He makes it a herald [nashiran] preceding His mercy, as He, the Glorified, said: 'And We send the fertilizing winds.' Thus, through its motion, the spirit [ruh] of the air reaches the animals and the plants, and they become prepared for growth. And if He wills, He makes it a punishment ['adhab] upon the disobedient from His creation, as God, the Exalted, said: 'Indeed, We sent upon them a screaming wind, on a day of unceasing calamity, plucking the people as if they were trunks of uprooted palm trees.'\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        "}},"20":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.35","c":"تَنْزِعُ","d":"ُʿعِznَt","e":"ia mencabut/menggelimpangkan"},{"b":"1.5","h":"2.23","c":"النَّاسَ","d":"َsāَّnlٱ","e":"manusia"},{"b":"3","h":"3.91","c":"كَأَنَّهُمْ","d":"ْmُhَّnَaʾَk","e":"seakan-akan mereka"},{"b":"5.0","h":"6.23","c":"أَعْجَازُ","d":"ُzāَjgْʿعَaʾ","e":"batang"},{"b":"6.1","h":"8.02","c":"نَخْلٍ","d":"ٍlْhkَn","e":"korma"},{"b":"7.6","h":"10.03","c":"مُنْقَعِرٍ","d":"ٍrِʿعَqnُّm","e":"tercabut/tumbang"}],"a":{"g":"Extracting the people as if they were trunks of palm trees uprooted."}},"21":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.85","c":"فَكَيْفَ","d":"َfْyَkَf","e":"maka bagaimanakah"},{"b":"0.79","h":"1.95","c":"كَانَ","d":"َnāَk","e":"adalah"},{"b":"1.4","h":"2.94","c":"عَذَابِي","d":"àِbāَhdَʿع","e":"azab-Ku"},{"b":"2.6","h":"5.02","c":"وَنُذُرِ","d":"ِrُhdُnَw","e":"dan peringatan/ancaman-Ku"}],"a":{"g":"And how [severe] were My punishment and warning."}},"22":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.25","c":"وَلَقَدْ","d":"ْdَqَlَw","e":"dan sesungguhnya"},{"b":"0.78","h":"1.48","c":"يَسَّرْنَا","d":"āَnْrَّsَy","e":"Kami mudahkan"},{"b":"2","h":"3.2","c":"الْقُرْءَانَ","d":"َnāَءْrُqْlٱ","e":"Al Quran"},{"b":"3.3","h":"5.44","c":"لِلذِّكْرِ","d":"ِrْkِّhdlِl","e":"untuk peringatan/pelajaran"},{"b":"4.3","h":"7.07","c":"فَهَلْ","d":"ْlَhَf","e":"maka adakah"},{"b":"5.0","h":"8.21","c":"مِنْ","d":"nِm","e":"dari"},{"b":"6.9","h":"10.04","c":"مُدَّكِرٍ","d":"ٍrِkَّdُّm","e":"orang-orang yang memikirkan"}],"a":{"g":"And We have certainly made the Qur'an easy for remembrance, so is there any who will remember?"}},"23":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"1","c":"كَذَّبَتْ","d":"ْtَbَّhdَk","e":"telah mendustakan"},{"b":"0.98","h":"2.37","c":"ثَمُودُ","d":"ُdwُmَht","e":"kaum Samud"},{"b":"1.9","h":"4.83","c":"بِالنُّذُرِ","d":"ِrُhdُّnlٱِb","e":"dengan peringatan/ancaman"}],"a":{"g":"Thamud denied the warning"}},"24":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.2","c":"فَقَالُوا","d":"۟āٓwُlāَqَf","e":"maka mereka berkata"},{"b":"2.1","h":"2.55","c":"أَبَشَرًا","d":"āًrَhsَbَaʾ","e":"apakah sesorang manusia"},{"b":"3.0","h":"3.84","c":"مِنَّا","d":"āَّnِّm","e":"dari antar kita"},{"b":"5.2","h":"6.37","c":"وَاحِدًا","d":"āًdِḥَٰw","e":"satu/sendiri"},{"b":"6.2","h":"7.72","c":"نَتَّبِعُهُ","d":"ٓۥُhُʿعِbَّtَّn","e":"kita mengikutinya"},{"b":"10.0","h":"11.65","c":"إِنَّا","d":"ٓāَّnِiʾ","e":"sesungguhnya"},{"b":"11.2","h":"14.24","c":"إِذًا","d":"āًhdِiʾ","e":"apabila"},{"b":"13.2","h":"14.92","c":"لَفِي","d":"àِfَّl","e":"benar-benar dalam"},{"b":"14.1","h":"16.3","c":"ضَلَالٍ","d":"ٍlَٰlَḍ","e":"kesesatan"},{"b":"15.3","h":"18.67","c":"وَسُعُرٍ","d":"ٍrُʿعُsَw","e":"dan dalam siksaan/gila"}],"a":{"g":"And said, \"Is it one human being among us that we should follow? Indeed, we would then be in error and madness.","ihya":"\n        <div class=\"ihya-tafsir-box\" style=\"margin-top: 15px; border-top: 1px solid #eee; padding-top: 10px;\">\n            <h5 style=\"color: #91740c; font-family: Cabin, sans-serif;\">Tafsir Al-Ihya</h5>\n            <div class=\"ihya-arabic\" style=\"font-family: IndoPak; font-size: 18px; text-align: right; margin-bottom: 10px; color: #555;\">\n                وقوله تعالى: ﴿ أبشرا منا واحدا نتبعه ﴾ فهذه المعميات هى التى منعت الاهتداء\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"ihya-english\" style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; color: #777;\">\n                Indeed, \"A human [bashar] from among us, one, shall we follow him?\" So these blindings [al-'amawiyyat] are what prevented the guidance [al-hidaya].\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        "}},"25":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.15","c":"أَءُلْقِيَ","d":"َàِqْlُءَaʾ","e":"apakah diturunkan"},{"b":"1.0","h":"1.84","c":"الذِّكْرُ","d":"ُrْkِّhdlٱ","e":"peringatan"},{"b":"1.8","h":"2.72","c":"عَلَيْهِ","d":"ِhْyَlَʿع","e":"atasnya/kepadanya"},{"b":"2.7","h":"4.23","c":"مِنْ","d":"ۢnِm","e":"dari"},{"b":"3.8","h":"5.18","c":"بَيْنِنَا","d":"āَnِnْyَb","e":"antara kita"},{"b":"4.9","h":"6.94","c":"بَلْ","d":"ْlَb","e":"tetapi/bahkan"},{"b":"5.3","h":"7.64","c":"هُوَ","d":"َwُh","e":"dia"},{"b":"5.8","h":"8.27","c":"كَذَّابٌ","d":"ٌbāَّhdَk","e":"pendusta"},{"b":"7.1","h":"10.58","c":"أَشِرٌ","d":"ٌrِhsَaʾ","e":"sombong"}],"a":{"g":"Has the message been sent down upon him from among us? Rather, he is an insolent liar.\""}},"26":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.5","c":"سَيَعْلَمُونَ","d":"َnwُmَlْʿعَyَs","e":"mereka akan mengetahui"},{"b":"1.6","h":"2.7","c":"غَدًا","d":"āًdَغ","e":"besok"},{"b":"1.9","h":"3.34","c":"مَنِ","d":"ِnَّm","e":"dari"},{"b":"3.7","h":"4.5","c":"الْكَذَّابُ","d":"ُbāَّhdَkْlٱ","e":"amat pendusta"},{"b":"5.1","h":"6.73","c":"الْأَشِرُ","d":"ُrِhsَaʾْlٱ","e":"sombong"}],"a":{"g":"They will know tomorrow who is the insolent liar."}},"27":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.4","c":"إِنَّا","d":"āَّnِiʾ","e":"sesungguhnya Kami"},{"b":"1.5","h":"2.07","c":"مُرْسِلُوا","d":"۟āwُlِsْrُm","e":"mengirimkan"},{"b":"2.3","h":"3.67","c":"النَّاقَةِ","d":"ِẗَqāَّnlٱ","e":"unta betina"},{"b":"4.1","h":"5.39","c":"فِتْنَةً","d":"ًẗَnْtِf","e":"fitnah/cobaan"},{"b":"5.1","h":"6.87","c":"لَهُمْ","d":"ْmُhَّl","e":"bagi mereka"},{"b":"5.9","h":"8.14","c":"فَارْتَقِبْهُمْ","d":"ْmُhْbِqَtْrٱَf","e":"maka tungguhlah mereka"},{"b":"7.5","h":"10.62","c":"وَاصْطَبِرْ","d":"ْrِbَṭْṣٱَw","e":"dan bersabarlah"}],"a":{"g":"Indeed, We are sending the she-camel as trial for them, so watch them and 